caption: Our #Werkself wins the DFB-Cup! 🏆 The crowning of Bayer 04 Leverkusen with the DFB-Pokal title comes just after securing the German championship title. With two titles and 51 games undefeated, this historic season comes to an end. Congratulations @bayer04fussball from everyone at #TeamBayer for the fantastic season well played! #ChampionsUnderTheCross #ForOurDream
